WEBVTT

00:01:59.062 --> 00:02:04.044
a circular room, nine sides,
nine entrances, nine paths,

00:02:06.036 --> 00:02:11.518
allowing you to come to the temple
from all directions,

00:02:11.542 --> 00:02:14.476
nine symbolizing completeness,

00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:15.740
perfection.

00:02:16.526 --> 00:02:20.040
No pulpit, no sermons,

00:02:20.064 --> 00:02:22.400
as there are no clergy
in the Bahá'í faith.

00:02:23.010 --> 00:02:27.115
And in a world which is putting up walls,

00:02:27.139 --> 00:02:30.587
the design needed to express in form